Bashneft, Tatneft May Get Tax Breaks as Early as 2012, RIA Says

-- B y   S t e p h e n   B i e r m a n
-- 
2011-09-27T13:23:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-27/bashneft-tatneft-may-get-tax-breaks-as-early-as-2012-ria-says.html
OAO Bashneft and OAO  Tatneft (TATN)  may
get mineral extraction tax breaks for some oil fields as early
as next year, RIA Novosti said, citing Sergei Shatalov, the
Russian deputy finance minister.  The Bashneft tax break may involve high-sulfur oil, while
the Tatneft break may apply to its Romashkinskoye field, RIA
said, citing Shatalov.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Stephen Bierman in Moscow 
 sbierman1@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
 Will Kennedy  at 
 wkennedy3@bloomberg.net . 